item.description:

item.title: I cant make my server online... Need Help
item.dc:creator: @kingman002 kingman002
item.description:
@kingman002 wrote:

don’t use hamachi. portforward using your router or download utorrent

if you have a router I can help you, if not download utorrent and there’s a utorrent guide with portforwarding.

With router:

click start, search cmd, click that, type ipconfig, go to internet, go to website ‘192.168.1.1’ click applications and gaming, make port 43594 to 43594, make sure its on BOTH, then type ur pv4 address, and click enable, save.

then u should make sure ppl have ur client, and make sure the client is ur ip, then ppl should beable to log in
